<h1>Superpower Health review<br>&#8212; <em>the honest version.</em></h1>
<p class="review-hero-sub">At $199/year, Superpower is the most aggressively priced comprehensive biomarker service in the market. Here&#8217;s what you actually get, what the &#8220;100+ biomarker&#8221; claim really means, and whether the price-to-value is as good as it looks.</p>
</section>

