<div>
<div class="verdict-title">Verdict: Best entry-level longevity panel on the market</div>
<p class="verdict-text">Superpower delivers a genuinely comprehensive biomarker panel at a price point that undercuts every meaningful competitor. The AI dashboard is polished, the included markers cover the longevity fundamentals, and the biological age score gives you something concrete to optimize toward. Honest caveats: one annual draw (not two), some of the advertised biomarker count is derived rather than directly measured, and the at-home draw option costs extra. For anyone starting a biomarker practice or on a budget, this is the right first step.</p>
</div>
